description: After Christmas sales always bring crowds into shopping malls. Including young people. So I decided to try my luck in one of those. It didn´t take me much time to find a real cutie. He was in a serious relationship but it didn´t prevent me from persuading him to jerk me off. He refused a similar offer in the past and was still regretting that. Which made things so much easier for me. If they say no, offer them more. We were just getting started in his car when some woman disturbed us. What a shame. Eventually, we ended up at his home. Thank god his girlfriend wasn´t there. She would be quite surprised at what her darling is willing to do for money. He looked almost happy about all the stuff I made him do.
title: Czech Hunter 230
